				Hi. I'm Jamie Lawrence, or J. I'm a web developer and designer, passionate music lover, gamer and 
				general dude from High Wycombe, UK. My skillset includes ASP.NET(C#), HTML(4/5), CSS(2/3), Javascript,
			 	jQuery, Ruby on Rails and extended knowledge of client and server side applications. My career has
				passed my by pretty quick so far, I currently work as a Team Leader in a Web Development department
